<div type="definition">
<p>LACK GUILT.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard idiomatic phrase for innocence is bù gū 不辜.</p>
<p>2. Wú zuì 無罪 is a very common periphrastic phrase for general innocence.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>無辜</p>
<p>無罪</p>
<p>清白無辜</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
